chapters.title: The green agenda is exacerbating Australia's wildfire problem
There is no link': the climate doubters within Scott Morrison's government
The Carbon Dioxide Theory of Climatic Change By GILBERT N PLASS

description:
Arson? Lack of hazard reduction? Nothing new? This video looks at what fire chiefs and scientists say is the REAL cause of the 2019-2020 fires in Australia, in response to amateur theories proposed by media commentators and bloggers. -- Potholer54

CORRECTIONS: 
1) The pronunciation of Bourke rhymes with 'Turk' not 'torque.' 
 
2) The police report on the screen shows 53 legal actions for failing to comply with the fire ban, I accidentally said 57 in the voiceover.

3) One poster has commented: "You said that 83% of hazard reduction burns have been carried out. But that was referring to all bushfire protection works mentioned, not just hazard reduction. 
The hazard reduction percentage is 76%." 
   I have not had time to verify this.
